results.name: a(n) = Product_{k = 1..n} A066841(k).
comment: Conjecture: a(n) divides A092287(n) for all n - see comments in A129365.
formula: a(n) = exp(Sum_{k = 1..n} log(k)/2 * floor(n/k) * floor(1 + n/k)). - _Daniel Suteu_, Sep 12 2018
program: (PARI) a(n) = prod(k=1, n, k^((n\k) * (1 + n\k) \ 2)); \\ _Daniel Suteu_, Sep 12 2018
